x+c
(x+c)(x+1)(x+2)=x^3+ax^2-bx+10
(x+c)(x+1)(x+2)=(x+c)(x^2+3x+2)=x^3+x^2(c+3)+x(3c+2)+2c
x^3+x^2(c+3)+x(3c+2)+2c=x^3+ax^2-bx+10
x,
2c=10\implies c=5
a=c+3=5+3=8
-b=3c+2=3\cdot5+2=17,b=-17
